OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FA man accused of breaching his ban on
OL,7,Fperforming liquid Brazilian Butt Lifts
OL,8,F(BBLs) has admitted the procedures
OL,9,Fwere not safe.
OL,11,FRicky Sawyer has appeared in court in
OL,12,FManchester, accused of breaking an
OL,13,Finjunction that bans him from carrying
OL,14,Fout BBLs or instructing, encouraging
OL,15,For permitting anyone to do them on his
OL,16,Fbehalf.
OL,18,FThis is the first time we have heard
OL,19,FMr Sawyer talk about his work in
OL,20,Faesthetics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FGary Lewis, counsel for Trafford
OL,7,FCouncil, asked Mr Sawyer: "Your
OL,8,Fwitness statement says 'I accept the
OL,9,Fcouncil's position that the procedures
OL,10,Fwere not safe', is that correct?"
OL,12,FMr Sawyer replied: "Yes."
OL,14,FHe also told the court on Wednesday
OL,15,Fthat he has no medical qualifications.
OL,17,FA liquid or filler BBL involves the
OL,18,Fpractitioner injecting usually 500-
OL,19,F1000ml of cosmetic fluid into the
OL,20,Fbuttocks, to make them appear larger
OL,21,For more round.
OL,26,@rD@aO]tD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FITV News has been investigating Mr
OL,7,FSawyer since 2023 after receiving
OL,8,Freports that a number of his clients
OL,9,Fneeded NHS treatment, battled
OL,10,Finfections and in at least one case,
OL,11,Fthe life-threatening condition sepsis,
OL,12,Fafter having a liquid BBL performed by
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FWatch: The moment ITV News confronts
OL,16,FRicky Sawyer after his court appearance
OL,18,FMr Sawyer admitted in court on
OL,19,FWednesday that there were complaints
OL,20,Fabout his conduct dating back to
OL,21,FOctober 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FWhen asked about the danger of the
OL,7,Fprocedure, he told the court: "There
OL,8,Fwas an element of, as with any
OL,9,Ftreatment, the risk and this was
OL,10,Fexplained to them (the clients)."
OL,12,FIn May 2025, Trafford Council
OL,13,Fsuccessfully applied to Manchester
OL,14,FCounty Court for Mr Sawyer to be
OL,15,Fforbidden from carrying out the filler
OL,16,FBBL or instructing, encouraging or
OL,17,Fpermitting anyone else to do so.
OL,19,FTrafford Council alleges he has
OL,20,Fbreached this ban, and Mr Sawyer is in
OL,21,Fcourt to defend this claim.
OL,26,@oD@_OUrD@SpmrD@_pnrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FIn his defence, Mr Sawyer claims he
OL,7,Fsold his company, which provided
OL,8,Fliquid BBLs to Lily May Silverman in
OL,9,FMay 2025, and has not been involved in
OL,10,Frunning it since.
OL,12,FHe added that he sold the business
OL,13,Fbecause he "didn't want the attention
OL,14,For the fuss that came with it any
OL,15,Flonger".
OL,17,FHigh-profile clients
OL,26,@uD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
