CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FMr Sawyer said "yes" and shrugged his
OL,7,Fshoulders when asked if he recalled
OL,8,FITV News coverage in 2024 that
OL,9,Freported he had received a prohibition
OL,10,Fnotice from Epping Forest District
OL,11,FCouncil preventing him from practising
OL,12,Fin the local authority area.
OL,14,FIn the report, ITV News found Mr
OL,15,FSawyer arriving in Canary Wharf,
OL,16,FLondon, outside the prohibition notice
OL,17,Fzone.
OL,26,@nD@POUnD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FWhen asked in court why, at the time,
OL,7,FMr Sawyer remained secretive about the
OL,8,Flocation of his appointments, he
OL,9,Freplied that it was because he had
OL,10,F"higher profile clients who didn't
OL,11,Fwant anyone to know where they are".
OL,13,FMr Lewis put to Mr Sawyer that it was
OL,14,F"to avoid detection of different local
OL,15,Fauthorities who had served a
OL,16,Fprohibition notice, not to protect
OL,17,Fwhere Katie Price was on any given
OL,18,Fday."
OL,20,F'The numbers don't add up'
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@AOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
