CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FMs Silverman, who Mr Sawyer claims
OL,7,Fpurchased the company The Clinic Club
OL,8,FLtd from him on May 16, 2025, was due
OL,9,Fto give evidence.
OL,11,FShe did not attend court on Wednesday.
OL,13,FWhen asked by Mr Lewis why this was,
OL,14,FMr Sawyer said: "I'm not in control of
OL,15,Fher, she doesn't owe me anything."
OL,17,F"She was unhappy she'd been brought
OL,18,Finto something that she wasn't aware
OL,19,Fof," he added.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
