CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FTrafford Council alleges Mr Sawyer
OL,7,Fnever formally sold the business, as
OL,8,Fhe remains the sole director of The
OL,9,FClinic Club Ltd.
OL,11,FWhen asked by Mr Lewis why there was
OL,12,Fno evidence of the #6,000 sale of the
OL,13,Fcompany, Mr Sawyer told the court: "I
OL,14,Fowed some money to suppliers, so she
OL,15,Fpaid that for me."
OL,17,F"How much did you owe suppliers?"
OL,18,Fasked Mr Lewis.
OL,20,F"#9,000," replied Mr Sawyer.
OL,26,@uD@dOUwD@RO]yD@AOUyD@aO]|D@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
