CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FTrafford Council also produced
OL,7,Fevidence of payments made by companies
OL,8,FMr Sawyer is the sole director of,
OL,9,Fsince the injunction was issued last
OL,10,Fyear, including #7,000 to Quiva
OL,11,FMedical, a company that sells filler,
OL,12,Fand #7,250 for advertising costs.
OL,14,F"The sale of this business is a
OL,15,Ffiction," Mr Lewis told the court.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
