OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FWhen later asked why #600 was paid
OL,7,Finto his company's bank account with
OL,8,Fthe reference 'Dr Ricky' on June 5
OL,9,F2025, Mr Sawyer replied: "I couldn't
OL,10,Ftell you why she put that, but it's an
OL,11,Finternational payment, so I wouldn't
OL,12,Fbe able to say when she made that
OL,13,Fpayment for it to be received on that
OL,14,Fday."
OL,16,F'Pleaded poverty'
OL,18,FMr Lewis told the court that Mr Sawyer
OL,19,F"pleaded poverty" in his witness
OL,20,Fstatement.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUvD@EO]{D@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
