PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779329020
OL,3,CBBL practitioner admits procedures
OL,4,Cwere not safe in court hearing
OL,6,FMr Sawyer agreed that the evidence
OL,7,Ftoday suggested he would receive, on
OL,8,Faverage, #1,500 per liquid BBL,
OL,9,Fperformed, in his words, "several"
OL,10,Ftimes a day, "three or four days" a
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FHe denied turning over tens of
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds a week and refuted
OL,15,Fthat he was happy putting the safety
OL,16,Fof individuals below that of his
OL,17,Ffinancial gain.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUqD@bO]rD@NOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
